{"tid":193424,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"新手想問youtube啲動畫係用咩software整","createTime":"2017-04-09T09:59:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-10T01:56:14.000Z","uid":76906,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"61fe99b87672b0a78587eb75659d4e5b63adf9ef","tid":193424,"uid":76906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T09:59:17.000Z","msg":"我本身識整flash，可以用flash整到類似呢類動畫:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Y7jEKYKEdbI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FY7jEKYKEdbI&d=wsLpXOxElywvcqXyO2fdBJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=8411424f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Y7jEKYKEdbI</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/A-qRnwyJM88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FA-qRnwyJM88&d=wsLpXOxElywvcqXyO2fdBJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=b28229f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/A-qRnwyJM88</a><br />\n<br />\n因為公司需要，想整類似呢種<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hf6apHaswsY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fhf6apHaswsY&d=wsLpXOxElywvcqXyO2fdBJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=dd6b783a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hf6apHaswsY</a><br />\n<br />\n但唔識點flash轉做mp4 up上youtube，同知道flash應該淘汰左，同埋見有啲YouTuber係可以動畫mix埋現實video，所以想問下係用咩software整。"},{"pid":"b45312c643aa363b9aa517f4c1c8f0d40739484f","tid":193424,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T10:00:47.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"6dafe21a03c06d9b9605c7c5bbd072b45e079528","tid":193424,"uid":61954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T12:23:38.000Z","msg":"flash新版？"},{"pid":"0f0104f8e57297505366ff7ffefa03e097c56e39","tid":193424,"uid":32402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T12:32:08.000Z","msg":"首先用Photoshop. Or illustrator 畫左個圖先再放去after effect到animate"},{"pid":"c85d503642d80bf4a15b66b95b5bc51e7ed6d392","tid":193424,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T12:35:35.000Z","msg":"其實D game既動畫係點整?<br />\n用咩software整??<br />\n<br />\n姐係好似三國無雙個D"},{"pid":"c28d3594782aab2b2db20ceb9758b945d9a4bb4f","tid":193424,"uid":32402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T12:41:02.000Z","msg":"Maya係主流3D既程式用黎modeling 之後export fbx就可以放入game engine<br />\n利申:學緊3D非專業"},{"pid":"55da53af9eeecc36e2b0c1fab29349dea0027e66","tid":193424,"uid":24788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T12:43:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Maya係主流3D既程式用黎modeling 之後export fbx就可以放入game engine<br />\n利申:學緊3D非專業</blockquote><br />\n樓主講個d係  after effect"},{"pid":"4e1c3332f39302ca4d6cbd23365aea234a1a3274","tid":193424,"uid":32402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T12:46:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Maya係主流3D既程式用黎modeling 之後export fbx就可以放入game engine<br />\n利申:學緊3D非專業</blockquote><br />\n樓主講個d係  after effect</blockquote><br />\n我上面講左用after effect 我係答問三國無雙個個巴打<br />\n無quote sor"},{"pid":"549a7f0d59d9eb399bcfec0ff6224b1542e84e4c","tid":193424,"uid":38316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:44:31.000Z","msg":"goanimate"},{"pid":"92317d1b01b7bd552fe22a5a54053a921f84a9da","tid":193424,"uid":76906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T14:11:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>首先用Photoshop. Or illustrator 畫左個圖先再放去after effect到animate</blockquote><br />\n唔該巴打，想問多少少，因為flash好易做動畫，但after effect就會麻煩好多同部機要好勁先run到。<br />\n有無咩簡單方法可以將flash動畫轉成mp4，或者同一般video合拼？<br />\n或者其他同flash相約嘅簡單動畫製作嘅software？"},{"pid":"00c742512624370e8566035a19c1ac971db1554e","tid":193424,"uid":32402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T16:03:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>首先用Photoshop. Or illustrator 畫左個圖先再放去after effect到animate</blockquote><br />\n唔該巴打，想問多少少，因為flash好易做動畫，但after effect就會麻煩好多同部機要好勁先run到。<br />\n有無咩簡單方法可以將flash動畫轉成mp4，或者同一般video合拼？<br />\n或者其他同flash相約嘅簡單動畫製作嘅software？</blockquote><br />\n我諗無咩人用flash咖啦，不過adobe既軟件通常都可以讀到，你可以試下用after effect or premiere開唔開到再export MP4 h264<br />\n如果你真係想認真整既話你係要學after effect，仲有after effect如果你唔係tracking基本上電腦唔洗話太勁"},{"pid":"4e7c9ce420c2d58bcf78b4cd2868a99b32c9bb09","tid":193424,"uid":33059,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T18:06:00.000Z","msg":"錄好你個flash 放上youtube<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f29fb2622aace19df081cc6be6f63e8eeefbbd1c","tid":193424,"uid":84780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T18:19:28.000Z","msg":"多數用flash ae 同ps去做 <br />\nps係整character <br />\nflash key frame <br />\nAe 加effect 字幕 <br />\n<br />\n題外話2d animation <br />\n多數都係用上面 或者坊間software做<br />\nFlash可以出mp4架 <br />\n出唔到都可以出其他檔 <br />\n用adobe encoder premiere去轉<br />\n利申 學緊3d animation"},{"pid":"7da4d2715a0ef025b46f3cbfa3f28fc33b6d7877","tid":193424,"uid":84780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T18:22:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多數用flash ae 同ps去做 <br />\nps係整character <br />\nflash key frame <br />\nAe 加effect 字幕 <br />\n<br />\n題外話2d animation <br />\n多數都係用上面 或者坊間software做<br />\nFlash可以出mp4架 <br />\n出唔到都可以出其他檔 <br />\n用adobe encoder premiere去轉<br />\n利申 學緊3d animation</blockquote><br />\n貼埋premiere 都可以剪聲加聲相對係咁好囉 <br />\n你公司有幾多筆直做 掉出去比人做 好過你唔識 <br />\n效果都相對好d"},{"pid":"1c74f1e2f60a15c732af0a0956378cb923dca6f8","tid":193424,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T18:43:36.000Z","msg":"thanks for answering<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實我乜都唔識，純粹好奇想學<br />\n<br />\n乜原來CG要咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LPOO2Ot-gdw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLPOO2Ot-gdw&d=wsLpXOxElywvcqXyO2fdBJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=6544e94b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LPOO2Ot-gdw</a>"},{"pi